title: Hyperbolic Complex Inverse Sine Function
description: This function calculates the hyperbolic inverse sine of a complex number using its real and imaginary parts. The function processes the input complex number and returns another complex number representing the result.
name: CASINH

input.name: X
input.description: A complex number for which the hyperbolic inverse sine is to be calculated.

return_value.description: The hyperbolic inverse sine of the input complex number.

fields.name: re
fields.description: The real part of the hyperbolic inverse sine result.

fields.name: im
fields.description: The imaginary part of the hyperbolic inverse sine result.
